Class ObjectNode

    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,SynNode>

    public class ObjectNode
extends SynNode
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,SynNode>
    Object node. Represents the result of a production with attributes.

    Implements Map<String,SynNode> for reasons of convenience. Modification attempts cause UnsupportedOperationException.
